==English==
===Etymology===
Anglo-Irish, from Irish [[piseog]] ‘witchcraft’, from Middle Irish [[piseóc]], [[pisóc]].

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /pɪ'ʃəʊg/

===Noun===
{{en-noun|pishogue|pishogues}}
# [[magic]], [[witchcraft]]; a [[spell]]
